headline: The 5 Most Interesting Analyst Questions From Labcorp’s Q4 Earnings Call
summary: Labcorp’s Q4 results came in below Wall Street’s revenue expectations, leading to a negative market reaction, while management attributed performance to strength in specialty testing and expanded partnerships with hospitals and regional labs.
